    "description": "Yugo Puzzle是使用果冻方块进行的2D益智游戏。透过拖曳可以使果冻左右跳动，相同颜色的两个果冻互相接触时就会合为一体。所有相同颜色的果冻都结合时，即可过关。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693260/extras/52b4abfab4d246c63fc2123d16157683.poster.avif?t=1769146249\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693260/extras/52b4abfab4d246c63fc2123d16157683.webm?t=1769146249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693260/extras/52b4abfab4d246c63fc2123d16157683.mp4?t=1769146249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>游戏规则单纯，但非常具有挑战性。起初甚至让人觉得可能无法过关。但透过反复尝试和失败，在逐渐找到方向后，突然间就会找到答案，这种时刻令人格外有成就感。<br><br>一开始你可能会对其难度感到惊讶，但请不要担心。随着游戏的进行，您会渐渐习惯。敬请享受各种独特又充满知性的谜题吧。<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 可使用深色模式和定制颜色 <br></li><li> 可显示或关闭果冻的表情 <br></li><li> 简约的谜题界面，让您可以专注在游戏上 <br></li><li> 跳动的果冻（游玩时的重要要素）</li></ul><br>您可以独自享受这个游戏，一边放松慢慢来；或者您也可以和朋友一起思考，获得更多乐趣。<br><br>希望您能喜欢这个游戏！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693260/extras/de0cca653685456e85fa7909353852ee.poster.avif?t=1769146249\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693260/extras/de0cca653685456e85fa7909353852ee.webm?t=1769146249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693260/extras/de0cca653685456e85fa7909353852ee.mp4?t=1769146249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693260/extras/ab5b29ff0f2fc015108b4b54d041bff6.poster.avif?t=1769146249\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693260/extras/ab5b29ff0f2fc015108b4b54d041bff6.webm?t=1769146249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1693260/extras/ab5b29ff0f2fc015108b4b54d041bff6.mp4?t=1769146249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
